This is a modification of a function included in the R package {forraGEO}.  
The function plots the temporal phenological spectra of a group of organisms using ah adjusted polynomial function over each group data.


Author original function:

Javier Valverde javi.val.mor@gmail.com

References

Valverde, J.; Calatayud, J.; Gómez, J.M. and Perfectti F. Variación intraestacional en los visitantes florales de Erysimum mediohispanicum en Sierra
 Nevada. Ecosistemas 2014 23 (3): 83-92.

